      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to allow a custodial parent a bad debt deduction for unpaid child support payments, and to require a parent who is chronically delinquent in child support to include the amount of the unpaid obligation in gross income.</title>
